---
description: Apple glass + Claude typography visual constraints for CCui GUI
globs:
  - "gui/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

## Visual duty (non-negotiable)

1. Never use pure black (#000). Darkest text: #1a1a1a or #1c1c1e.
2. No decorative emoji in navigation or chrome. Use SVG icons (stroke 1.5).
3. One accent color (#d97757) for primary actions and selection. No rainbow UI.
4. Animation: cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1). No bounce unless scroll rubber-band.
5. Spacing: 4px grid. Section gaps >= 2x internal gaps.
6. AI reply body: serif (Charter/Georgia). UI chrome: SF Pro system sans.
7. Prefer shadow layering over 1px gray borders on cards.
8. Message layout: Claude document style, not chat bubbles.
